{"tid":1485071,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"（接力愛国）陳錦鴻：守護香港 周海媚：不能再亂下去了","createTime":"2019-08-18T15:28:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T10:11:52.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":86,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"cbed272df1414b78782962c89c95937aeeebfa7c","tid":1485071,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190818/_2019081816014439194.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190818%2F_2019081816014439194.jpg&h=ed596127&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《逃犯條例》修訂引發連串風波愈鬧愈激烈，香港多位藝人佘詩曼、楊千嬅、蔡少芬與丈夫張晉、陳法蓉、陳曉東、朱茵、鄧萃雯等均已表態愛國愛港。<br />\n<br />\n央視新聞今早在微博發放周海媚接力守護香港的片段，說：「香港的局勢牽動人心，無論如何香港不能再亂下去了。我在香港出生、成長、工作，中國是我的祖國，香港是我家。我愛中國，我愛我家。希望香港盡快恢復安寧、平靜、和諧。」<br />\n陳錦鴻稍早亦有拍片稱：「我愛中國，我愛香港。每一個中國人都應該守衛香港。我愛我的祖國。」另外，陳松伶今早在微博發文：「我是中國人，我以此為傲」。惠英紅前夜也有發文「#香港是中國的香港#！加油中國加油香港」。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1570522/即時-娛樂-接力陳錦鴻守護香港-周海媚-不能再亂下去了</code></pre>"},{"pid":"3019cca2e13ba552155041ab9b1c66c3a065e40d","tid":1485071,"uid":34334,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:55:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19408a77107cc45d1dba9cac21a0e8a073f17cea","tid":1485071,"uid":299372,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:32:54.000Z","msg":"平時人模人樣<br />\n一到大是大非d狗態盡現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"111d8a4604576ed4e431ce30ffaed60bb99fbca6","tid":1485071,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T22:52:10.000Z","msg":"公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bde52bef4a60bb19afdbff84207c076c0e16789","tid":1485071,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"111d8a4604576ed4e431ce30ffaed60bb99fbca6",